/**
 * Define component of route in src/navigation/routes
 */

const AppRoute = {
  LOGIN: 'Login',
  SIGNUP: 'Signup',
  FORGOT_PASS: 'ForgotPass',
  HOME: 'Home',
  PROFILE: 'Profile',
  SEARCH: 'Search',
  MEDICAL_REC: 'MedicalRecord',
  BOOKMARKS: 'Bookmarks',
  NOTIFICATION: 'Notification',
  SCHEDULE: 'Schedule',
  CATEGORY: 'Category'
}

export { AppRoute };
